This is '''LuaRocks''', a deployment and management system for Lua modules.

LuaRocks allows you to install Lua modules as self-contained packages called "[[Types of rocks|rocks]]", which also contain dependency information. LuaRocks supports both local and remote repositories, and multiple local rocks trees.

* '''[[Download|download]]''' and install LuaRocks on [[Installation instructions for Unix|Unix]] and [[Installation instructions for Windows|Windows]].
* '''[[Documentation]]''' available from this wiki.

LuaRocks is free software and uses the same [[License|license]] as Lua.
